data.description: LOCATION - LOCATION -PRIVATE, QUIET and MOVE-IN Ready! Located on a cul-de-sac on a LARGE .26 acres lot close Colington Harbour main entrance. This updated 3 bedroom,1.5 bath Beach Box features a NEW roof, 3 NEW pilings, NEW paint and NEW floors, remodeled bathrooms and updated appliances. Upstairs you have an open kitchen and living area with a full bathroom in the hallway, master bedroom with half bath and another bedroom. An office area leads to the downstairs area which includes another bedroom and bonus room with laundry area. A huge backyard offers room for a huge garden or backyard play. Ready for you to create your Outer Banks memories. Additional improvements include; new corner/sun deck, concrete driveway, landscaping throughout. Colington Harbour offers a large outdoor Community pool and tennis courts for an additional fee. You will adore this home - Take a look today!
